<topic id='element_correspondence_address.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: CORRESPONDENCE ADDRESS - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>an175 (5 lines each an35)</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_correspondence_address">CORRESPONDENCE ADDRESS</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_address">ADDRESS</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_correspondence_address">CORRESPONDENCE ADDRESS</xref>
 is the correspondence 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_address">ADDRESS</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_address_structured">ADDRESS STRUCTURED</xref>
) nominated by a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
, where the 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_address_association_type">ADDRESS ASSOCIATION TYPE</xref>
 is National Code 
    <i>'Correspondence (Non-Residence)'</i>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_correspondence_address">CORRESPONDENCE ADDRESS</xref>
 will consist of 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_building_name">BUILDING NAME</xref>
, 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_building_number">BUILDING NUMBER</xref>
, 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_street_or_road_name">STREET OR ROAD NAME</xref>
, 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_post_town">POST TOWN</xref>
, 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_postal_county">POSTAL COUNTY</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_referral_request">REFERRAL REQUEST</xref>
, a contact address is specifically for that referral. This allows any correspondence about the referral to be directed appropriately. The 
    <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_correspondence_address">CORRESPONDENCE ADDRESS</xref>
 need not be the initiator's practice address.  </p>


  </body>
